txt.en: 'Now that the fish are healthy again, would you consider joining us in the great pursuit? We'll give you a fair share on anything you catch!'
'I am grateful for these. We always need more good quality fish such as these, so come back tomorrow if you fancy a little more coin.'
Now that the fish are healthy again, Umaris has asked for your help feeding the village. Bring her a mix of healthy fish for a reward.
